{"tid":1844734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖][香港獨立] 呢場運動可以點行落去?","createTime":"2020-01-26T18:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T19:44:03.000Z","uid":310858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0d3940b3684a5b871e1ffa8745b653c4fdab75","tid":1844734,"uid":310858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"FF下如果呢刻香港已經獨立左<br />\n我地已經可以自行決定封關, 我地已經可以唔駛再受中共擺佈<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地可以救番好多條人命</span><br />\n<br />\n我知而家我地未有公開嘅agenda去獨立<br />\n加上而家行出街都隨時瀨野既時候, 街頭抗爭更加困難<br />\n但咁樣唔等於我地無野可以做<br />\n<br />\n其中重要嘅一環一定係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span></span><br />\n以下係幾點建議/提醒:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 文宣係人人都可以做! 唔係淨係期望文宣組會做野 <br />\n<br />\n2. 文宣可以有唔同形式: 識整圖就整圖, 唔識圖嘅就打字, (根據非正式研究指出) 你求其打堆字再cap做圖其實已經好易spread同埋好吸睛, 當然記得要fc fc fc<br />\n<br />\n3. 港獨文宣唔係淨係一開口就話要脫離支那, 要多角度好多<br />\n入手方向可以有2個: (1) push factor, (2) pull factor</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1X0e6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1X0e6p.jpg&h=2919e9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上建議只係拋磚, 如果有不足請大大力屌<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益, 諗下武漢肺炎期間呢場運動要點繼續生存落去<br />\n覺得有用請推!!<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立, 刻不容緩!<br />\n香港獨立, 香港獨立!"},{"pid":"5d543d7ce6b7e533a04c3923f24c643dd85e5de7","tid":1844734,"uid":303052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9LhhtW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9LhhtW.png&h=6359a7be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOwPS2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOwPS2g.jpg&h=18856b97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fac6e5adb897603cd0e516bbd8afc6d7c9155cdb","tid":1844734,"uid":315669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T19:17:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b80a28319bd6c3f93cf7902632ee1933a6aff471","tid":1844734,"uid":56311,"l